dcterms:description: JetNet is a Python library specifically designed to enhance accessibility and reproducibility in machine learning research within the field of high energy physics, focusing on particle jets. It includes jets from Gluons, light quarks, top quarks, W bosons, and Z bosons, characterized by various particle and jet features.
dcterms:title: JetNet
